\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray}
\{a_{minor},a_{major}\} & = & \frac{\sin\varphi}{\sqrt{1\pm\cos\varphi}}.\label{ellipse4}
\end{eqnarray}

\end_inset

The eccentricity 
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon\equiv\sqrt{1-(a_{minor}/a_{major})^{2}}$
\end_inset

 is therefore approximately equal to 
\begin_inset Formula $\sqrt{\left|\cos\varphi\right|}$
\end_inset

 as 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|\cos\varphi\right|\rightarrow1$
\end_inset

.
 
